Text: Anyone know if this is a demo or the full version?
It appears to be the full version from what I can tell so far.  I can't imagine LegendET would put a demo up without stating so in the title or description...always a high quality uploader.

After downloading and extracting I start game and am able to watch first cut video and get to main screen to enter my name.  After hitting "Play", though, I just get a black screen with a red box/frame in the center.  Any ideas?
